data.description: Welcome home to this completely updated and gorgeous Colonial! Brand new trendy vinyl plank flooring graces each and every room. An open concept floor plan provides for a generous areas for living room relaxation and comfortable dining area that connects to the new kitchen. Updated and sparking best describes this kitchen with new quartz counter tops, new stainless steel appliances and abundance of white cabinets. The full bath has also been updated with new shower/tub, new vanity and is large enough for washer and dryer. Each of the 3 bedrooms are on the upper level, all freshly painted in soft pastels and have vinyl plank floors. There is additional finished space in the walk out lower level, with some of the space heated. Great potential for many different uses from home office, family room or personal gym. Other updates include a new roof, new vinyl siding and new driveway. All you will need to do, is move in and enjoy!
